<br>
Warrior, joust the fuk ar, heal, nuke, dot..Bow kite if you really want to, this guys not going to live if he sticks around.<br>
<br>
Rogue, AHAHAHA, Ds + Dot + 1 nuke and there toast 'if' they stick around (I'm keeping in mind most people don't get snared on my pvp server unless they are caught offguard.)<br>
<br>
Monk, Only tough one I can think of simply due to dmg output and trainq staff but then against, the casting still pounds em and you have sow/heals/dispells, monks not going to last that long.<br>
<br>
Paladins, ..rofl. <br>
<br>
Beast Masters , ..rofl.<br>
<br>
