<br>
Druids - There DS is annoying, there dots are annoying, and there sow is annoying, but guess what..Golem wands destroy druids entirely, pumice is pretty good too, you 'have' to dispell against druids, in the end, you'll find that the ranger will in fact cap the druid - really depends on your fr and if the druid has two insta cast items..thats always a bitch.<br>
<br>
Bards - They just run, so who cares?<br>
<br>
<br>
Leaves us with the Shadow Knight, whom - is always a rough and tumble battle of wits, decisions and luck..Oh and don't forget gear. <p>Green~~Ninja (sc)
Green-Ninja{Imp} (ut/cs)
Clearrain/Clearain (eq vz server)</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uulynvindix.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ulyn Vindix</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/7/02 7:02:54 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=648.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Fear doesnt work on PVP servers (against players).</span><hr size=1> Horses, and spell crits never a problem?  I like rangers, mind.<br>
